Show HN: ChatGPT in Telegram with roles, search, images and voice
text:
Hello, my name is Denis

@talkgptbot

ChatGPT in Telegram with character roles (girlfriend, toxic, drunkard, coder, etc), input as a voice message (Google speech-to-text), synthesis based on search engine SerpAPI results for factoid questions + image generation with StableDiffusion. You can switch between modes for different use cases, for example, use search always or be a programmer.

Please share the feedback!

We started a month ago and made it with GPT3.5 + DeepL for translation, now we don't use translation at all as seems Turbo is cheaper and translate quite well.

I will create 1 FREE website for you
text:
Hello HN,

I have a plan to create 1 free website for anyone who need a website but he/she/? couldn’t afford it. I want to do it only for 1 person in each country.

Why I am doing this? First- marketing purpose Second- international work experience and improve my communication skills Third- make people happy and make new friends

The website you are going to order should be a simple website with 3 pages; homepage - about page - contact page. I will do it with WordPress and I will teach you how to manage it at the end. I will give you the best advices to choose a suitable cheap hosting plan + domain (no hidden affiliate) - you have to buy the hosting+domain from wherever you prefer - I just offer free website creating and customize it base on your needs. You have to provide me the website data - pictures - logo (if any) - videos and anything you want to put on your website.

So, If you need a website and can’t afford the service fee (or if you know someone, please share), I am here, ready to help you. Please give me the right to accept or reject your requests. Please consider, I am going to create 195 websites for 195 individuals, So I need to schedule. Base on your request-time you may sit at the end of the waiting-list. You have to be patient !.!

My website is : https://ebastiban.com

Please contact me via the Email on my website, or put your comments here.
